#: static/custom/templates/introduction.html:10
#: static/sample/templates/introduction.html:10
msgid "home.introduction.message"
msgstr ""
"This atlas provides you with the whole wild species observed in the "
"territory. Each new observation feeds in real time the sheets of each "
"species you consult, in a desire to share and enrich knowledge about "
"biodiversity. <br/> <br/>This atlas presents observations carried out "
"under different scientific protocols. This is not an exhaustive inventory"
" nor a complete distribution of species in the territory."

